# ============================================================
# Public workflow: drought traits, vegetation greening, and TAC trend
# ============================================================
#
# Purpose
# -------
# This script outlines the main analytical workflow used to test whether
# drought-history traits are associated with changes in vegetation local
# recovery dynamics, represented here by the trend in lag-1 temporal
# autocorrelation (TAC).
#
# Main questions
# --------------
# 1. Are drought frequency, mean severity, and mean duration associated
#    with the TAC trend after controlling for climate, vegetation state,
#    and broad spatial structure?
# 2. Do these drought effects differ across vegetation greening-rate
#    classes?
#
# Notes for public release
# ------------------------
# - Replace the placeholder paths in Section 1 with your own data paths.
# - Large raster inputs are not included in this repository.
# - Project-specific local paths, figure styling details, and manuscript-
#   specific polishing code have been removed.
# - This script is intended as a transparent workflow template rather than
#   a fully plug-and-play reproduction package.
# ============================================================


# ------------------------------------------------------------
# 0. Packages
# ------------------------------------------------------------

